{"tid":2218654,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公務員事務局設立機制　容許同性配偶可享公僕福利","createTime":"2020-09-26T11:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T11:37:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"589734771194c28feeff92aacd5561509c7386a7","tid":2218654,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局表示，已設立機制，讓公務員申報其在香港境外締結的同性婚姻，以及申領相應的已婚公務員福利。<br />\n<br />\n當局在回覆人民力量立法會議員陳志全的信件提及，因應已婚同性伴侶申請公務員配偶福利上訴得直的案件，局方表示，已設立機制讓公務員申報及申領福利，會因應終審法院的裁決及命令，處理每宗申請，安排細節已透過便箋通知各部門。<br />\n<br />\n高級入境事務主任梁鎮罡早前不滿，他的同性婚姻伴侶不能享有公務員家人福利，及跟伴侶共同評稅，提出司法覆核，原訟庭裁定他在配偶福利方面勝訴，但被上訴庭推翻，梁鎮罡上訴至終審法院得直，判詞裁定政府的決定涉及歧視成份，下令撤銷有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n另外梁鎮罡爭取合併評稅的部分亦獲判勝訴，稅務局網頁列明，在有關案件作出裁決後，就《稅務條例》而言，同性婚姻會被視為有效婚姻。任何已婚人士，不論是異性或同性婚姻，均有權與配偶選擇合併評稅；並有權根據《條例》就其配申索免稅額或扣稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551807-20200926.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551807-20200926.htm&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=3b1d02dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551807-20200926.htm&h=c93671d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551807-20200926.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f377e090ff58270c33d638885c3d83397642a41d","tid":2218654,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9558c65d6a9d0e32ed5bb4e77250c37e893e6c19","tid":2218654,"uid":89267,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"正，男人求其搵麻甩佬去外國注冊結婚，咁就可以拿到宿舍"},{"pid":"6c8e6923703b31725fb1dcc266351b217f762850","tid":2218654,"uid":218082,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9558c65d6a9d0e32ed5bb4e77250c37e893e6c19","tid":2218654,"uid":89267,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"正，男人求其搵麻甩佬去外國注冊結婚，咁就可以拿到宿舍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁你都可以就咁是旦搵隻支那雞結婚再拎宿舍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港大撚把異性戀走去假結婚呃福利啦on9"},{"pid":"559a74e3b7fa3ca264219d72733980e63f9cb830","tid":2218654,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"收買人心"},{"pid":"06d0ae285ebe51141017bbd1c14ebc1825308ee8","tid":2218654,"uid":89267,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6c8e6923703b31725fb1dcc266351b217f762850","tid":2218654,"uid":218082,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9558c65d6a9d0e32ed5bb4e77250c37e893e6c19","tid":2218654,"uid":89267,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"正，男人求其搵麻甩佬去外國注冊結婚，咁就可以拿到宿舍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁你都可以就咁是旦搵隻支那雞結婚再拎宿舍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港大撚把異性戀走去假結婚呃福利啦on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"女人比較麻煩，男人好d"},{"pid":"716b630f0b5e416ec3d5504bb322c4ae3bcb1357","tid":2218654,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"無得同性結婚<br />\n<br />\n但係又可以有同性配偶"},{"pid":"d207bb074c3edf14478fc382728015ec3f35b9d3","tid":2218654,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"咁有冇侍產假"},{"pid":"3f1a29f3bd7b383151f50de532b0a61988786af4","tid":2218654,"uid":317305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}